Thierry Henry Set to Face Arsenal With Red Bulls in Emirates Cup in July

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-04-28T12:04:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/thierry-henry-set-to-face-arsenal-with-red-bulls-in-emirates-cup-in-july.html
Ex-Arsenal striker  Thierry Henry  is
set to play against the Gunners after his New York Red Bulls
team was named today as one of four clubs in the pre-season
Emirates Cup.    Paris Saint-Germain and Boca Juniors are the other teams
joining hosts Arsenal in the July 30-31 event in  London .     Henry, 33, played for the Gunners between 1999 and 2007,
scoring a club-record 226 goals in 370 appearances. He moved to
Barcelona before switching to the Red Bulls last year.       To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  